snippet.textDisplay: Ngl, as much as I love Doom Eternal and the way it requires you to think quick and act even quicker, the marauder is pretty fucking annoying. I don’t know if it’s because the games new and still has some kinks, or maybe I’m just not paying enough attention but for some goddamn reason the mf almost never drops his shield during the fight, even when I’m at mid range. It’s possible to make an enemy a difficult one to kill without making it an annoying asshole that doesn’t listen to the rules of its own fighting system
snippet.textOriginal: Ngl, as much as I love Doom Eternal and the way it requires you to think quick and act even quicker, the marauder is pretty fucking annoying. I don’t know if it’s because the games new and still has some kinks, or maybe I’m just not paying enough attention but for some goddamn reason the mf almost never drops his shield during the fight, even when I’m at mid range. It’s possible to make an enemy a difficult one to kill without making it an annoying asshole that doesn’t listen to the rules of its own fighting system
